# 🏋️‍♂️ AI Fitness Agent (Computer Vision)

**AI Fitness Agent** is a real-time posture and workout tracking system that uses **OpenCV + MediaPipe** to analyze body movements during exercises like **Squats** and **Push-ups**.  
It provides **instant feedback**, counts **reps**, and detects **form errors** — like a virtual trainer right in your webcam!

---

## 🚀 Features
- 🧠 Real-time full-body pose estimation using **MediaPipe**
- 🔢 Automatic rep counting (Squats / Push-ups)
- ⚠️ Posture feedback (e.g., torso lean, knee-over-toe, hip misalignment)
- 💻 Works with any webcam
- 🔄 Easily extensible for new exercises

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- **Python 3.8+**
- **OpenCV** – frame capture & drawing
- **MediaPipe** – body pose detection
- **NumPy** – math operations
- *(Optional)* TensorFlow / PyTorch – for custom models

---

## ⚙️ Installation
```bash
git clone https://github.com/<your-username>/AI-Fitness-Agent.git
cd AI-Fitness-Agent
pip install -r requirements.txt
